OL,3,CWhat is the Lampard mental health
OL,4,CInquiry?
OL,6,FNamed after its Chair, Baroness Kate
OL,7,FLampard CBE, The Lampard Inquiry is a
OL,8,Fstatutory inquiry, investigating the
OL,9,Fdeaths of inpatients who died whilst
OL,10,Fthey were living on adult and children
OL,11,Fmental health units run by the NHS in
OL,12,FEssex, between the years 2000 and the
OL,13,Fend of 2023.
OL,15,FIt will also look at deaths that
OL,16,Fhappened within three months of
OL,17,Fpatients being discharged from those
OL,18,Funits.
