OL,6,FIt is an important difference for some
OL,7,Ffamilies and campaigners, who were
OL,8,Funhappy with the original, non-
OL,9,Fstatutory inquiry, the Essex Mental
OL,10,FHealth Independent Inquiry - which
OL,11,Fstarted in 2021, but had to be
OL,12,Fabandoned after only 11 members of
OL,13,Fstaff, out of the 14,000 that were
OL,14,Fcontacted, agreed to give evidence.
OL,16,FDuring the inquiry, Baroness Lampard
OL,17,Fwill hear evidence from bereaved
OL,18,Ffamilies, former patients, experts and
OL,19,Fstaff.
